<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="such-pron">such <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sʌtʃ/    美 /sʌtʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>这样的人 / 事物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Such were her words. 
这些就是她所说的话。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Such was Einstein, a simple man of great achievements.
这就是爱因斯坦，一个简朴而又取得伟大成就的人。</p></div>

<p>注: 为加强语气，such位于句首时主语和谓语用部分倒装语序。  </p>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="such-as">such as</h3>
<p>1.<strong>诸如；例如：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cartoon characters such as Mickey Mouse and Snoopy are still popular.
像米老鼠和史努比这样的卡通人物仍然很受欢迎。</p></div>

<p>注: such as常用来进行列举，并直接放在列举的名 词之前。for example表示“例如”，用来举例说明某一情况或论点，可放在句首、句中或句末。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She does well in many subjects such as mathematics, physics, and chemistry.
她许多学科的成绩都很好，比如数学、物理和化学。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His spelling is terrible! For example, look at this word.
他的拼写太糟糕了，例如，就看看这个单词吧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mexico, Canada, and China, for example, all have oil reserves.
例如墨西哥、加拿大和中国，都有石油储备。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong><em>_</em></strong>_ is the power of TV that it can make a person suddenly famous.  （2009 辽宁）<br />
A.Such<br />
B.This<br />
C.That<br />
D.So  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. A  </p></div>